{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_02_05",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 02 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "1、2、3、4――もっと指先に気を遣う！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four――Pay more attention to your fingertips!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_clap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "天動さん、キレがないわよ！　メリハリ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san‚ you lack sharpness! More emphasis!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "endTime": 8.299999809265136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――グランプリに向けて三人は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The three of them are working even harder than before‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.5,
      "endTime": 11.299999925825329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これまでよりさらに厳しいレッスンに励んでいた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "training for the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2999999258253,
      "endTime": 15.699999809265112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "奥山さんはもっと体を使って！　大きく、広く！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san‚ use your body more! Big and wide movements!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.9,
      "endTime": 19.99992789067328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "鈴村さん、テンポズレてるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san‚ your timing’s off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20,
      "endTime": 22.11165542602539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3,
      "endTime": 23.391337847709657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.923963972926106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ひーん……レッスンめっちゃ厳しいなぁ\n今までの練習がぬるま湯に思えてくるわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… The lessons are so tough.\nOur previous practices feel like taking a lukewarm bath now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 33.9666664759318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……でもこれまで以上に\n上達している手ごたえもある……楽しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know… But I also feel like\nwe’re improving more than ever before… It’s fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 40.175532786051434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "私も！　コーチのことも大好きだし！\n毎日、おしるこご馳走してくれるもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too! I love the coach!\nShe makes us red bean soup every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.38692291722154,
      "endTime": 46.58692301258897,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "それはアメとムチ戦法やと思うけど……\nせやけど、おしるこって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that’s more of a carrot and stick approach…\nBut red bean soup…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.786922917221524,
      "endTime": 52.83692291722153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そういう所が、すみれのいい所よね\nずっとこのままでいてね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what’s so great about you‚ Sumire.\nStay that way‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.03154657313549,
      "endTime": 58.01621797511303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　あれ？\n私、何か変なこと言っちゃった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? What?\nDid I say something weird?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.19821323980217,
      "endTime": 62.72914309133415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ううん、別になにも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not at all…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.92418198355491,
      "endTime": 65.19610938795859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　そうやって子供扱いして！\n絶対私、変なこと言っちゃったリアクションじゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! You’re treating me like a child!\nThat’s totally the reaction you give when I say something weird!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.57418207892235,
      "endTime": 72.16155180701072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……休憩だって言ってるのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I said it was break time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.34660391577539,
      "endTime": 74.84660391577539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そこまで騒げるほど元気が有り余ってるとは、ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but you have so much energy to spare that you’re making that much noise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.84660391577539,
      "endTime": 79.35712561377343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.56464612594559,
      "endTime": 80.51407926193191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さあ、立ちなさい三人とも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ get up‚ all three of you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.71407926193191,
      "endTime": 82.81407916656448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "ダンスコーチB",
      "speakerNameEn": "Dance",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "望み通り練習再開するわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll resume practice as you wish!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.81407926193194,
      "endTime": 85.21407907119705,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2833.333237965917,
          "startTime": 85.64741249989785
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3332379659114,
          "startTime": 86.24741249989785
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4140791665645,
      "endTime": 88.93995216003374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 89.98074583323115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は隣のスタジオにも\n練習してるアイドルがおるみたいやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like there are some idols practicing\nin the studio next door.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.34741249989786,
      "endTime": 96.16117688130655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "時々音が聞こえるから、まだいるみたいね\nそれがどうかしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can hear sounds sometimes‚ so it seems like they’re still there.\nWhat about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3490593573239,
      "endTime": 101.25588470903898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと練習、覗いていかへん？\n敵情視察ってことで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why don’t we go take a peek at their practice?\nYou know‚ for reconnaissance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.47095315676593,
      "endTime": 106.00018213015458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、それいいかも！\n私も気になってたんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that sounds fun!\nI’ve been curious too~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.20428649009929,
      "endTime": 110.87594195427164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、今日はもう練習も終わったし\nこの後の予定もないし、少しなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we’re done practicing for today‚\nand we don’t have any plans afterwards‚ so I guess it’s fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.07095315676607,
      "endTime": 116.92433173876681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_02_05-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "満場一致やね！\nほんなら、着替えてさっそく見に行きましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s unanimous!\nAlright‚ let’s get changed and go see them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1376198234327,
      "endTime": 121.78761972806527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 123.00428649009902
